title: Don't Be A Complainer
itunes:title: Don't Be A Complainer
description:
In this message, Victoria will teach us why we should not complain. God says, “Rejoice always, pray continually, give thanks in all circumstances; for this is God’s will for you in Christ Jesus” (1 Thessalonians 5:16–18 NIV). Let’s keep our mouths closed, stay the course and be grateful to God. Let’s not be faultfinders. Let’s be those who pray and petition God for change with thanksgiving in our heart.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
